transcript:

Customer: Nahi woh galti se lag gaya tha.
Executive: Accha accha toh sir aapko phone kar raha hai ji sir ji sir ji sir ek concern raise hua hai toh mai close kar du sir?
Customer: Haan close kar dijiye.
Executive: Okay sir sir ek feedback usko sir aap positively de dena sir jaisa aapko lage.
Customer: Haan.
Executive: Theek hai sir okay sir.
